		<region region-id="3257" left="6" top="30" width="454.5" height="272.25" align-x="6" align-y="42" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
			<text use-page-width="false" push-down="false" lock-width="true">
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Для определения шума вентилятора необходимо знать следующие параметры:</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit"/>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Расход воздуха через вентилятор...............................<region region-id="41" left="312.75" top="60.75" width="56.25" height="19.5" align-x="337.5" align-y="72.75" show-border="false" show-highlight="true" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="#80ff80" tag="">
						<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
							<ml:define xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
								<ml:id xml:space="preserve" subscript="в">G</ml:id>
								<ml:real>282</ml:real>
							</ml:define>
						</math>
						<rendering item-idref="2"/>
					</region> кг/с</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit"/>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Адиабатический напор..............................................<region region-id="265" left="312.75" top="96" width="101.25" height="26.25" align-x="342" align-y="114.75" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
						<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
							<ml:define xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
								<ml:id xml:space="preserve" subscript="ад">H</ml:id>
								<ml:apply>
									<ml:mult/>
									<ml:real>2.413</ml:real>
									<ml:apply>
										<ml:pow/>
										<ml:real>10</ml:real>
										<ml:real>4</ml:real>
									</ml:apply>
								</ml:apply>
							</ml:define>
						</math>
						<rendering item-idref="3"/>
					</region> Дж/кг</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit"/>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Коэффициент полезного действия в вентиляторе......<region region-id="44" left="314.25" top="138" width="59.25" height="19.5" align-x="338.25" align-y="150" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
						<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
							<ml:define xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
								<ml:id xml:space="preserve" subscript="в">η</ml:id>
								<ml:real>0.82</ml:real>
							</ml:define>
						</math>
						<rendering item-idref="4"/>
					</region>
				</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit"/>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Диаметр вентилятора.................................................<region region-id="45" left="315" top="173.25" width="60" height="19.5" align-x="339.75" align-y="185.25" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
						<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
							<ml:define xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
								<ml:id xml:space="preserve" subscript="в">D</ml:id>
								<ml:real>2.31</ml:real>
							</ml:define>
						</math>
						<rendering item-idref="5"/>
					</region> м</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit"/>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Частота вращения вала...............................................<region region-id="88" left="318" top="208.5" width="60" height="19.5" align-x="339.75" align-y="220.5" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
						<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
							<ml:define xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
								<ml:id xml:space="preserve" subscript="в">n</ml:id>
								<ml:real>2676</ml:real>
							</ml:define>
						</math>
						<rendering item-idref="6"/>
					</region> об/мин</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit"/>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Плотность воздуха на входе в вентилятор...................<region region-id="260" left="318.75" top="250.5" width="64.5" height="19.5" align-x="341.25" align-y="262.5" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
						<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
							<ml:define xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
								<ml:id xml:space="preserve" subscript="в">ρ</ml:id>
								<ml:provenance expr-id="1">
									<originRef doc-id="271890E4-301A-4BFE-875D-2E2C22D76D26" version-id="8AABAD4E-4013-4F8F-BE80-69C3472D15D6" branch-id="00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" revision-num="237055796" is-modified="true" region-id="20212" href="C:\Users\Baybal\Desktop\Компрессоры\КНД(Вентилятор).xmcd" xmlns="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/provenance10">
										<hash/>
									</originRef>
									<parentRef doc-id="271890E4-301A-4BFE-875D-2E2C22D76D26" version-id="8AABAD4E-4013-4F8F-BE80-69C3472D15D6" branch-id="00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" revision-num="237055836" is-modified="true" region-id="20212" href="C:\Users\Baybal\Desktop\Компрессоры\КНД(Вентилятор).xmcd" xmlns="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/provenance10">
										<hash/>
									</parentRef>
									<comment xmlns="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/provenance10"/>
									<originComment xmlns="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/provenance10"/>
									<contentHash xmlns="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/provenance10">9545bff156674eb89441e8034b8e5c58</contentHash>
									<ml:real>0.878</ml:real>
								</ml:provenance>
							</ml:define>
						</math>
						<rendering item-idref="7">
							<element-image-map>
								<box left="34.5" top="0.75" width="30" height="15" expr-idref="1" xmlns="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/worksheet30"/>
							</element-image-map>
						</rendering>
					</region> кг/<region region-id="263" left="403.5" top="243.75" width="15" height="23.25" align-x="410.25" align-y="262.5" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
						<math optimize="false" disable-calc="false">
							<ml:apply xmlns:ml="http://schemas.mathsoft.com/math30">
								<ml:pow/>
								<ml:id xml:space="preserve">м</ml:id>
								<ml:real>3</ml:real>
							</ml:apply>
						</math>
						<rendering item-idref="8"/>
					</region>
				</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit"/>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">Скорость звука............................................................<region region-id="1000" left="318.75" top="282.75" width="67.5" height="19.5" align-x="344.25" align-y="294.75" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
